---
const nav = [
  { label: "Inicio", href: "/" },
  { label: "Servicios", href: "/services" },
  { label: "Sobre Nosotros", href: "/about" },
  { label: "Testimonios", href: "/testimonials" },
  { label: "Contacto", href: "/contact" },
];

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-8 border-t border-slate-200 bg-white/95">
  <div class="container-page py-12">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">
          <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-50 ring-1 ring-brand-100">
            <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="YDreams Health Services" class="h-8 w-8 rounded-lg object-cover" />
          </span>
          <span>YDreams Health Services</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm text-slate-600">
          Atencion de enfermeria a domicilio con profesionalismo, calidez y protocolos de seguridad clinica.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs font-medium text-slate-500">Redes sociales: disponibles pronto.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Navegacion</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
          {nav.map((item) => (
            <li>
              <a class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900" href={item.href}>
                {item.label}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Contacto</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li><span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Telefono:</span> +829-843-6803</li>
          <li><span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Email:</span> ylandacaetam@gmail.com</li>
          <li><span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Direccion:</span> Calle Caonabo #69, sector Gazcue</li>
          <li><span class="font-medium text-slate-800">Horario:</span> 24/7 (segun servicio)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-slate-200 pt-6 text-xs text-slate-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <p>(c) {year} YDreams Health Services. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <p>Cuidado responsable y privacidad desde el primer contacto.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
